{"tid":938971,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣先可以冇咁憎自己男朋友","createTime":"2018-12-12T17:16:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T06:52:42.000Z","uid":164264,"like":28,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"409a7dbdfc59382cf6c73bde42ca5f68098ab6b2","tid":938971,"uid":164264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:16:41.000Z","msg":"成日都好憎自己男朋友<br />\n唔知係我小氣定點<br />\n但一諗到佢以前講大話又約人扑野嗰啲<br />\n我就會心情好差 好影響我一整日既運作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即使佢依家貌似變乖左 都會因為啲小事就刺激到我<br />\n最後我自己又發脾氣收場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想自己成為一個比男朋友覺得煩 什至係討厭既女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上其實我發脾氣都發到好攰...<br />\n我究竟可以做啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"825e65d5ad9895a4fdd6a71b0d0a3ff4569a7fcc","tid":938971,"uid":218638,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:29:31.000Z","msg":"飛左佢啦 不忠只會接二連三"},{"pid":"96ecc1d18eb1c92410c2cda9d032444d55b6dfc5","tid":938971,"uid":201604,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:32:49.000Z","msg":"點解要同佢拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be818fcbbfa6ed8c726db5591abf09e18b67b106","tid":938971,"uid":164264,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"96ecc1d18eb1c92410c2cda9d032444d55b6dfc5","tid":938971,"uid":201604,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:32:49.000Z","msg":"點解要同佢拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:36:48.000Z","msg":"因為同佢一齊開心既時刻真係好難忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即使依家成日嘈但佢都仲係好努力咁帶啲開心比我<br />\n所以搞到我都好懷疑自己係咪太小氣太敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd9c1a43926bf073f9a181b6cf8b01bb819d030","tid":938971,"uid":6285,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:36:50.000Z","msg":"分手啦<br />\n以前發生過嘅事如果放低唔到 唯有分手啦<br />\n相信你自己都知遲早一係你疑心太重你哋會成日鬧交<br />\n一係佢真係衰多次<br />\n既然咁唔開心 長痛不如短痛"},{"pid":"2f27ea4b96bec1cfd8ab1fa5ee46a859710bf525","tid":938971,"uid":197887,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:37:05.000Z","msg":"冇架 心裡面一路記住佢之前做過既事<br />\n明明耿耿於懷 但又放唔開<br />\n睇返自己以前都唔係一個會亂發脾氣既人<br />\n因為男朋友犯過錯 成日好敏感 好易胡思亂想 <br />\n少少事都觸動到神經發脾氣<br />\n就會好討厭自己 究竟點解會搞到今日咁"},{"pid":"92ee019070d0b49058f10ae770056d11a1d14210","tid":938971,"uid":21355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:37:23.000Z","msg":"分手"},{"pid":"e14cd590f23fcba7ba24ec99d151811efaadf78b","tid":938971,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:38:01.000Z","msg":"好事嚟"},{"pid":"287b5320ef49ebad22c2d49790a9b07898451df4","tid":938971,"uid":164264,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fd9c1a43926bf073f9a181b6cf8b01bb819d030","tid":938971,"uid":6285,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:36:50.000Z","msg":"分手啦<br />\n以前發生過嘅事如果放低唔到 唯有分手啦<br />\n相信你自己都知遲早一係你疑心太重你哋會成日鬧交<br />\n一係佢真係衰多次<br />\n既然咁唔開心 長痛不如短痛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:39:50.000Z","msg":"就係好想搵辦法去放低過去既野 <br />\n但我真係做唔到 <br />\n所以越嚟越覺得自己廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時真係覺得自己因為佢而穿左個窿<br />\n或者可以話係physically存在 <br />\n但入面已經爛曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca7e68d60f42101e689254ed8039932dac28fb18","tid":938971,"uid":162406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"287b5320ef49ebad22c2d49790a9b07898451df4","tid":938971,"uid":164264,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fd9c1a43926bf073f9a181b6cf8b01bb819d030","tid":938971,"uid":6285,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:36:50.000Z","msg":"分手啦<br />\n以前發生過嘅事如果放低唔到 唯有分手啦<br />\n相信你自己都知遲早一係你疑心太重你哋會成日鬧交<br />\n一係佢真係衰多次<br />\n既然咁唔開心 長痛不如短痛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:39:50.000